作者 | 江晓川 出品|棱镜·腾讯小满工作室欢迎下载腾讯新闻APP，阅读更多优质资讯中国卫生部门指定的核酸检测试剂盒生产企业正在加班加点，以期满足不断进展的疫情需要。
Welcome to download Tencent News APP and read more high-quality information. China's health-sector-designated Nucleic Acid Testing Kit manufacturers are working overtime to meet the growing needs of the epidemic.
一家国家卫健委指定采购企业的员工告诉《棱镜》，目前“全公司员工自发回公司，不回家过年了。
An employee of a state health care commission appointed by a purchasing company told Prism that "the whole company's employees spontaneously return to the company, do not go home for the New Year.
”核酸试剂盒用于新型冠状病毒（2019-nCoV）的检测，但不涉及治疗。
Nucleic acid test kits were used to detect the new coronavirus (2019-nCoV), but did not involve treatment.
此前的报道称，湖北当地由于缺乏检测试剂盒，多名肺炎感染患者无法确诊。
Previous reports said that Hubei due to a lack of test kits, many patients with pneumonia could not be diagnosed.
在国家卫健委向各地下发的关于新型冠状病毒感染肺炎的确认程序中，明确各省级疾控中心可向上海辉睿、上海捷诺以及上海伯杰三家公司采购核酸检测试剂盒。
In the confirmation procedure of the new coronavirus infection pneumonia distributed by the National Health Care Commission, it was made clear that the provincial CDC could purchase nucleic acid test kits from Shanghai Pfizer, Shanghai Teno and Shanghai Berger.
有要求匿名的试剂盒研发企业表示，目前“全公司三班倒，每天10万人份的产量已经是极限。
At present, "three shifts a day for 100,000 people is the limit," said the company, which requires anonymity.
”三家试剂盒生产企业均在对外发货上海伯杰在一份公告中称已经准备了2019年新冠状病毒相关的核酸检测试剂，以及半自动和全自动提取仪等产品。
All three kits were shipped out of the country. Shanghai Berger said in a statement that it had prepared new coronavirus-related nucleic acid reagents for 2019 and products such as semi-automatic and fully automatic extractors.
上海本地媒体的报道显示，伯杰已经在向外地用户发货。
Local media reports in Shanghai showed Berger was already shipping goods to customers outside the city.
国资委新闻中心“国资小新”称，上海捷诺“首家成功研制出新型冠状病毒核酸分子检测试剂盒，并已送至中国疾控中心验证…试剂产品已经供应到全国大部分省份，包括香港和澳门地区。
According to SASAC News Centre, Shanghai Teno "was the first successful development of a new coronavirus nucleic acid molecular detection kit, which has been sent to China CDC for verification... reagent products have been supplied to most provinces of the country, including Hong Kong and Macao.
”上海捷诺是国药集团中国生物的下属公司。
Shanghai Tenero is a subsidiary of China Biology, the Chinese drug group.
上海辉睿的工作人员称，目前咨询核酸试剂盒采购的单位众多，应接不暇。
Shanghai Pfizer staff said that the current advisory nucleic acid kit procurement units are numerous, overwhelmed.
这家公司在2015年与中国疾病预防控制中心联合推出了中东呼吸综合征冠状病毒检测试剂盒。
The company in 2015 and the Chinese Centers for Disease Control and Prevention jointly launched the Middle East respiratory syndrome coronavirus detection kit.
研发成功到上市或需绿色审批核酸试剂盒属于医疗器械，上市前须经过药监部门审批。
Successful R & D to the market or green approval of nucleic acid test kits is a medical device, prior to listing must be approved by the Department of Pharmaceutical Supervision.
资深医疗投资人告诉《棱镜》，“众多上市公司公告中提到的‘研发成功’不代表就能上市，疫情紧急可以走绿色通道审批，申请产品注册证。
Senior medical investors told Prism that the "success of R & D" mentioned in the announcements of many listed companies does not mean that it can be listed on the market.
”此前，包括硕世生物、华大基因、西陇生物及科华生物等上市公司均表示研发成功了针对新型冠状病毒的核酸检测试剂盒，其中部分公司表态向多个省级疾控中心供应。
Previously, listed companies including Masters, Huada Gene, XiLong Biology and Kohwa Biology all indicated that they had successfully developed nucleic acid test kits for the new coronavirus, with some of these companies offering supplies to provincial CDC.
国家药监局1月22日表态称，将做好应急审评审批准备，根据法律法规要求和工作需求，“随时启动疫情防控所需药品、医疗器械的应急审评审批。
The State Administration of Pharmaceutical Supervision and Administration said on January 22 that it will make preparations for emergency review and approval, and in accordance with the requirements of laws and regulations and the requirements of the work, "start the emergency review and approval of drugs and medical devices needed for disease control at any time.
”一个案例来自广东，医疗器械供应商“奥咨达”表示，其客户广州安捷用于预防呼吸道飞沫及空气传播疾病患者隔离的医用隔离床“苦战3天2夜”，获得了药监部门审批。
In one case from Guangdong, OZDA, a medical device supplier, said its client, Guangzhou Anjie, had been approved by the drug watchdog for "three days and two nights of hard work" to prevent respiratory droplets and airborne diseases.
这是广东省药监局参照《医疗器械应急审批程序》做出的首个有条件快速审批案例。
This is the first conditional rapid examination and approval case made by Guangdong Pharmaceutical Supervision Bureau with reference to the Emergency Approval Procedure for Medical Devices.
风险投资机构东方富海的合伙人陈华伟推测，目前核酸试剂盒产能爬坡困难的原因之一，在于春节假期，缺乏生产人手，疫情的猛然进展也使得原材料采购变得艰难。
Chen Huawei, a partner at Orient Wealth Management, a venture-capital firm, speculates that one of the reasons for the current difficulty in climbing capacity is the lack of production staff during the Spring Festival and the sudden advance of the disease has made the procurement of raw materials difficult.
卫健委《确认程序》中还表示：确认程序在中国疾控中心或第三方检测机构接到检测标本后24小时内完成；第三方检测机构为华大基因。
The confirmation procedure is completed within 24 hours after receiving the specimen from the China CDC or a third party testing organization, which is the Huada gene.
一家检测机构的工作人员告诉《棱镜》，第三方检测机构主要提供检测服务，通过质量流程控制，确保试剂盒检测结果的准确性。
A staff member of a testing organization told Prism that third-party testing organizations mainly provide testing services, through quality process control, to ensure the accuracy of test kit test results.
言下之意，试剂盒检测可能存在结果不准确的情况。
The implication is that the test kit test may have inaccurate results.
了解试剂研发的科研人员说，理论上核酸检测试剂盒的技术是成熟的，原理也明确，因此这次研发速度很快。
Researchers with knowledge of reagent development say that the development of nucleic acid test kits is, in theory, mature and based on clear principles, so the pace of development is fast.
但需要注意的是，检测存在假阴性和假阳性的情况，有可能消耗更多试剂盒做重复检测。
It should be noted, however, that the detection of false-negative and false-positive cases has the potential to consume more test kits for repeated testing.
